==English==

===Etymology===
From the specific, trademarked name for a brand of refrigerators.

===Pronunciation===
AHD: frĭj'ĭ-dâr'

===Noun===
# a refrigerator
#: ''He [...] had everything necessary to the Modern Man, / A phonograph, a radio, a car and a frgidaire.'' -- ''The Unknown Citizen'' by W.H. Auden.